Package org.sibermatica.io

Class Data

java.lang.Object
org.sibermatica.io.Data
@Deprecated(since="1.4") public final class Data extends Object
Deprecated.
This class manages high quantities of bytes, and it is low-performance because it uses long values

Data

Is is used for converting byte size, for this purpose this contains instances representing the size in bytes, and methods that convert the byte size in the required byte size.
Byte size are:
  • Byte
  • Kilobyte
  • Megabyte
  • Gigabyte
  • Terabyte
  • Petabyte
Since:
1.0
Author:
Ciro Alejo Diaz
